# --- Secrets: never commit real credentials (match anywhere in the tree) ---
**/.env
**/credentials.txt
**/secret.yaml

# --- Python / virtualenvs ---
**/.mlflow
**/.venv
**/venv
__pycache__/
*.pyc

# --- MLflow local runs / artifacts ---
**/artifacts/
**/mlruns/
mlartifacts/

# --- Database / artifact dumps (back these up out-of-band, not in git) ---
*.dump
*.sql

# --- Large binaries / caches ---
*.cache

# --- Generated by the example script ---
confusion_matrix.png
